instructions =
(
---All---
Ctrl+T = Look up highlighted text in telephone directory
Win+Click = Ctrl + Printscreen (used for Greenshot)
Ctrl+Esc = Restart
Ctrl+Shift+Esc = Quit

---EMIS---
Shift+F1 = Find user / Reset password
Ctrl+L = Type out clipboard
Win+Shift+E = Extract xml files to a location. Assumes save dialogue is in correct location already
Win+Shift+P = Save Template as a word printout. Assumes save dialogue is in correct location already
Ctrl+Shift+V = Care Summary view Term Properties code adder. Assumes: you've copied the list of codes, top down, from the xls sheet
"gogetcon " = Save consultation (in full) as a word document
"gosetcon " = Attach document to user. Assumes path to document is in clipboard

---Templates---
Editing a template:
Win+Shift+S = Update component "section" (uses clipboard e.g. "h"="History" section)
Win+Shift+C = Change section to "Create components as children" with Free text entry

Code Selector/Code Pick List:
Ctrl+A = Add all codes from selected to the bottom
Ctrl+Shift+V = add in read codes from list in clipboard (copied from Word template). Optionally select the header
Ctrl+Shift+Alt+V = add in clipboard list of codes

Clinical Code Properties:
Ctrl+Shift+V = paste in single code from clipboard

Text Pick List Properties:
Ctrl+Shift+V = paste multiple text list values from Clipboard (copied from ord template)
Ctrl+Shift+P = paste in the prompt, then values after

---Word---
"goadd" = Add clipboard entries to EMIS Document: Legacy Drop-down Form Field
Control+Shift+C = Copies and cleans the word output from EMIS template
)